info:
  title: BrAPI
  version: ''
openapi: 3.0.0
paths:
  /variantsets:
    get:
      summary: Gets a filtered list of `VariantSets`.
      description: Will return a filtered list of `VariantSet`.
      parameters:
        - name: variantSetDbId
          description: The ID of the `VariantSet` to be retrieved.
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: variantDbId
          description: The ID of the `Variant` to be retrieved.
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: callSetDbId
          description: The ID of the `CallSet` to be retrieved.
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: studyDbId
          description: Filter by study DbId
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: studyName
          description: Filter by study name
          in: query
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/page'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/pageSize'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/authorizationHeader'
      responses:
        '200':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/VariantSetsListResponse'
        '400':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/400BadRequest'
        '401':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/401Unauthorized'
        '403':
          $ref: '#/components/responses/403Forbidden'
      tags:
        - Variant Sets
components:
  responses:
    VariantSetsListResponse:
      description: OK
      headers: {}
      content:
        application/json:
          schema:
            title: VariantSetsListResponse
            type: object
            required:
            - metadata
            - result
            properties:
              '@context':
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Context'
              metadata:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/metadata'
              result:
                title: VariantSetsListResponseResult
                type: object
                required:
                - data
                properties:
                  data:
                    items:
                      $ref: '#/components/schemas/VariantSet'
                    type: array
